msg: finish remove support.  Split CFS.resolve() into resolve(), which combines ColumnFamilies, and removeDeleted(), which takes a single ColumnFamily and returns a new one with deleted IColumns removed. Keep deletion information around until removeDeleted is called so that deletion information can properly supress older IColumns.
